    • environment.logic.entities.Entity

      • detectHit

        public static boolean detectHit(Entity entity1,
                                Point finalPosition,
                                Entity entity2)
        Checks if a specified Entity will collide with another specified Entity before it reaches a specified Point from the first Entity.
        Parameters:
        entity1 - The first Entity.
        finalPosition - The Point that denotes the final position of the first Entity.
        entity2 - The second Entity.
        Returns:
        true if a collision is detected between the two specified Entitys and false if not.
